journalArray.text:
very well that you completed all targets
need more focus during the day. away from visual studio
Do not take rest of cereals from Filip in the evening please. Decision to stop sugar completely without exception. Sugar is useless and can be replaced by fruits and a full lot of other joys.

moni was sick so I took care of filip for his bath. Then I phoned to mum and finished at 08:45 pm. I took this as an excuse to not only not go for a walk, but also not do any pushups. As a result I failed on both and also fell asleep in front of tv, and then could not go to sleep until 3am...

Regarding work: found out that in the office I have more energy because I am not constantly alone in my room and because the environment is changing and because I talk with colleagues (other subjects than autism and problems with kids).

Not reading the news starts to have a positive impact on my morale
yesterday I took two biscuits from filip ( filip had a full box). Then took two other ones to take with tea

Did not do the meditation in the morning, then I had no time during work. In the evening with Filip it was impossible. Filip was very calm in the evening and it was amazing. He went to bed early but I forgot to do the missing meditation. So no meditation on that day. Good focus at work, but my ability to focus could be better.
Too much netflix in the evening? replace by what?
tłusty czwartek + once again, did not do meditation in the very morning and then busy at work

Great regularity. Thanks to this, stronger and stronger at pushups and better at mindfulness (although netflix seems to be a problem )
New problem with consumption of sugar.

Took bread with honey 3 times in the evening. Because there was nothing else to put on the bread and because filip was shouting. Should replace by 15 times 45 deg pomps or meditation
Good regularity for the rest

did not sleep enough because of filip. Managed to keep good focus in the morning but the afternoon was tough. 
all habits fulfilled !!! 
10 min meditation disturbed by netflix

Habits put in place and maintained with the tool seem to have a significant impact on the way I feel.
I managed to fulfill everything today, well done! no sugar was good. 
Had great discipline to stop netflix at 1130 so slept not too bad (amount was ok and I was able to walk in the morning)

Better at work. I had a constructive discussion and were more patient at explaining. That is how I should be: patient at explaining. It is the better way for the other person to understand. Filip difficult in the evening and monika took cakes from a box and I plunged into it. Good that I did not exagerate, but I need to make the  decision that it is simply not food.
Spent a lot of time reading the news on my mobile. Influence on morale, stress and concentration. Also, big loss of time.
Monika bought a lot of cakes for the holydays. Looked at news on hindustan times on mobile. Very good regularity on pushups

Work + returning of Dominik very tough. Monika and me escaped for a moment and watch netflix. Was feeling several times in a day that I am missing something, I need to compensate my situation with something nice, and that is how I finally eat bread with honey. Next time try the pushup technique, or read about react.

Day with Filip extremely tough. Kept calm. Managed to fulfill all habits. Negative thoughts  about him, about application not working well on mobile, about geopolitics. But still habit to try to come back to present moment. Thought about increase number of meditation during week-ends
Said no to my Moni giving me a pond-check. Well done. Then when going to the cinema, resisted the temptation to take a cake at the star bucks before the film. Well done!!!

Feeling down all afternoon, then terrible meeting. Wanting to quit. Frustration of role being more like servant than manager and career arriving to an end. The same evening Filip was giving problems in evening and not getting to sleep until midnight.
Feeling a bit better. Day at office. Also on Sunday listened to music instead of netflix and  also went to bed before 11pm. Good candidate for a next habit, as well as ONE  focus time

scenario alone with Filip on weekend, Monika coming back with cakes and I eat them. Also in the morning I watch netflix to feel better. As a result no meditation + cakes.
What I should  do in that case is that I meditate first thing in the morning while I still have the energy to do so.
For the cakes I do not know, maybe it should  be an exception.

Greatly disturbed by the war in Ukraine and the possible consequences. Managed to do 100%, that is great. Once  all good  with sugar, think about going from 10min medit to two times 10min on some days at least.
Today a lot of pushups done :) . Also did back exercises with my chair. Meditation done; was very difficult to concentrate, but tried. All targets met :). Starting to get use to avoid deserts :)
News on mobile -> less concentration overall, fear. Must stop watching it on mobile. Enough to ear radio while washing dishes.

Constipation followed by blood. Stressful. Changed habit no sugar no peanut from Monday to not done ( I took over type of peanuts, which may be the source of problem). Also liquid should not be with milk. Are not going to Indian restaurant so regularly and using so much milk regularly. Feeling bad about all this history in the search team and how I did not make it to director. Starts usually when I am sitting in the search team. Should cut more and sit in the global marketing area. Also, it was a good move to go to my new boss's team. She has a better ethic and I am starting from scratch, but on a better basis. So I should just be PATIENT.

Very difficult day with dominik disappearing from home while he was sick,  and Filip breaking a mug in the middle. Evening difficult with Filip. My attitude was not a disaster, but still I lost my positivity.
Well done to fulfill everything, especially the desert part after the problem occurred. It would be good to be able to work on positive attitude.
Monika gave me a cake

Manage a day without desert although biscuits were lying on the table and moni took two deserts.
Good job!

Good that I manage with sugar during 10 days. In fact I only need to act in the moments when someone gives me a desert. Then I must systematically say no thank you. Very stressful weekend with D. I told her what I think about her presence during the weekend. She does not understand that in our situation we need encouragement and not critic.

Good that I did not take any cereals. just walked around ;)
Decent concentration at work. Watched documentary on Elon Musk and how his company's learning is based on failure.
Read news on mobile very briefly, but still, I could have avoided completely by checking out hindi vocabulary instead.

A lot of meetings today, and one got me frustrated. I often get frustrated at meetings. 
At the end of the day I was so fed up I took biscuits and a lot of chocolate.
Other things are going ok in terms of habits, but I have a problem with sugar again. It seems I never get more than 2 days streak

During weekend, friends came, ate a lot of cakes and then took the 2 leftover cakes on Monday. It seems that to fulfill the objective of reducing sugar, the only way is to stop completely! Push ups great, can see changes in my body. Started squats. Thinking about the following additions: once a week make the exercises at the gym, + meditation twice on saturday or sunday
Can replace sugar desert by what I call "koło ratunkowe". I made a list that I put in my bedside table.  Filip made such a fuss that I did not go to walk. Take off Saturday from this habit.
Monika put cakes on the table and said they were with special corn. Still counts as sugar.

Good regularity except sugar. A lot of exception when going out with Monika. At work good concentration but less meeting. I know the best work for me is work where I do more than I meet. Except if the  meeting is to solve a technical problem.
Tough day with Filip. Managed to keep my calm, smile under difficult moments. And managed to fulfill all  habits. Well done!
A lot of pushups lately, very good. Next habits is either one focus moment, sleep at 11:30 or once per week at gym or without tv.
At costa took special tee which had probably even more sugar than ten cakes. Plan is to stop from tomorrow completely. At parties I do not take cake. At costa I take normal tee with milk.
ok to eat a cake when invited, but not ok to eat 3 :) So I do not mark the "no  sugar" as done. Regarding pushups, did the minimum on Sunday, but did more on Saturday.
Monka gave the cake to me while I was working and I could not resist. In the afternoon I had big problems to concentrate.

Managed to do everything :) 
A little bit less pushups, but still above minimum agreed.
At work, very difficult to concentrate, but did a good job. No touch to visual studio, very good !
No sugar: on a good path, keep it up!

All done, great :) As usual I was able to do more pushups than planned. 
Good that I did not take any desert ( although took black chocolate)
I can see an impact of this sustained discipline on my body and how I feel physically.
Spent too much time on netflix in the evening . Missed the next morning walk because of this. Should stop at 11pm. Even if Filip is not sleeping yet.
Watched too late netflix in the evening: very tired during the afternoon. 11h30 is the max.
I made a decision to stop sugar, so I should just stop. When I get a cake I just say no thanks. When there is a party I take only one. Simple rule.
Everything done, well done !! A lot of effort put at work. Efficient use of kolo ratunkowe
Regularity in pushups. Feeling strength. Regarding news, should stop altogether, limiting to newspaper on weekend

All habits done, well done! Managed to go for a walk first thing in the morning.
No sugar twice in a row. Technique to do mini pushups instead of desert is working.
I feel good physically. 
Managed to help Filip stop his crisis in the evening! Being more positive and watching TV with him and commenting with him.
